summary: Adjusts some of the MihailMods creatures and monsters mods for Requiem use.
descriptionHtml:
Being a huge fan of Mihail creatures and monster mods and requiem i thought that it could be a good idea to make them compatible. I haven't patched a lot of them yet but i'll be making them as much as i can.
